<div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[640px]">
  <div class="surface-card relative isolate overflow-hidden rounded-[36px] px-5 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(79,134,255,0.16),transparent_35%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,rgba(67,199,184,0.18),transparent_36%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-70">
      <div class="absolute left-[12%] top-[20%] h-px w-[30%] bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#4F86FF,transparent)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-[35%] top-[54%] h-px w-[36%] bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#43C7B8,transparent)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-[18%] top-[78%] h-px w-[42%] bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#FF9B62,transparent)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-[24%] top-[18%] h-[58%] w-px bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,#D96B88,transparent)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-[62%] top-[34%] h-[46%] w-px bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,#4F86FF,transparent)]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
      <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-white/70 bg-slate-950/[0.03] p-4 shadow-inner shadow-slate-900/5">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <div class="h-2 w-24 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
            <div class="h-2 w-16 rounded-full bg-slate-100"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#4F86FF]"></span>
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#43C7B8]"></span>
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#FF9B62]"></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <div class="workflow-node workflow-node-blue float-slow">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500">入口</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">读取资源与节点上下文</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-[14%] workflow-node workflow-node-mint float-slower">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500">分组</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">整理条件分支与关键路径</p>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-node workflow-node-orange">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500">调试</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">确认模板、字段与执行反馈</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
        <div class="surface-subcard float-slow">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-blue-600">节点搜索 / AI 补全</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">先找到节点，再让建议结果落回可视化上下文。</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700">模糊搜索</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700">建议补全</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="surface-subcard float-slower">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-emerald-600">LocalBridge / 本地能力</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">文件、截图、OCR 等本地入口按需启用，不挤占首屏叙事。</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">文件管理</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">截图识别</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="surface-subcard">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-orange-600">模板 / 调试 / OCR</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">模板与调试信息聚合在同一工作台里，避免来回切屏。</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-700">调试面板</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-700">模板复用</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
